# Personal key dates (add-on config)

Copy this file to `/share/daily_briefing/key_dates.md` on first install.
Non-standard dates to flag — birthdays, anniversaries, etc. Standard US
holidays are computed in code and don't need an entry here.

Format: `- MM-DD — Description [for: gary|shannon|both]`
Tag omitted = `both`.

<!-- - 03-14 — Shannon's birthday -->
